# What will (likely) be the title of your project?

Guess the word game

# In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "My project a web-based synthesizer.")

My project will be a platform for a game we play with friends which we usualy write a lot of words on paper and split to 2 teams and in turns one member of each goes and pick a random word and tries to make his team understand the word using only pantomime, i want to build a software that can save the use of paper and instead use a software to generate random words for the players to pantomime.

