# In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

its going to be a HTML website using java script and css, there will be a timer for each player of 1 minute, every time he starts the timer goes off, you can press generate a word and it will generate a word from an array, you can also skip a word, when the count of the words end the game will present "game over" 

